Sanditi Virtual Try-On
An open-source virtual try-on system designed for fashion brands, developers, and apparel businesses to digitally visualize garments on models.
🚀 Features
Upload garment images and model images
Apply garments onto models digitally
Lightweight and fast processing
Built for real-world fashion and ecommerce use
🧠 Use Cases
Preview designs before physical sampling
Reduce sampling and production costs
Enhance e-commerce product visualization
Assist designers in rapid prototyping
💼 Real-World Usage
This system is actively used in a production workflow for apparel development and digital sampling.
